<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.11">
<l>tīrnta vaṭiyavar tammait tiruttip paṇikoḷḷa valla</l>
<l>vārnta pukaḻac cutaṉai yamarar pirāṉai yemmāṉai</l>
<l>vāynta vaḷavayal cūḻtaṇ vaḷaṅkuru kūrccaṭa kōpa</l>
<l>ṉērntavō rāyirat tippattu maruviṉai nīṟu ceyyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These ten in the one thousand granted</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from cool fertile Kurukūr surrounded by excellent fertile fields</l>
<l>on our lord the lord of immortals, the unshakable one with fame that is full,</l>
<l>who is capable of correcting the devotees who come to an end [and] take [them] in service,</l>
	<l>will make difficult karma into ashes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
